  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>Enjoy the best of the Norwegian fjord’s glorious and diverse scenery in this exclusive 4-centre group tour, escorted by a knowledgeable guide throughout. Designed as an excellent introduction to Norway for those wishing to see the spectacular fjords, mountains, glaciers and lakes in four contrasting destinations - from the historic city of </span><a data-udi="umb://document/d517b2c21fa94eb096a3bcb6b7e933c5" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/bergen" title="Bergen">Bergen</a><span> to the serene Sognefjord, and from the glacier arms in Loen to the Atlantic coast in </span><a data-udi="umb://document/4796d8535a46439d92020f8a158e7c03" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/alesund" title="Alesund">Ålesund</a><span>. This tour gives you an insight into the ‘real’ Norway where even your transfers between resorts are spectacular scenic day trips.</span></p>
<div>
<p><strong>Maximum Group Size: </strong>30</p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/highlights-of-the-fjords#Tour highlights">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/highlights-of-the-fjords#itinerary">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/highlights-of-the-fjords#Your holiday includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/highlights-of-the-fjords#Hotels">Hotels</a>| <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/highlights-of-the-fjords#departure dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
